name: Frumster
overview:
Frumster was originally created in December 2001, to help Orthodox Jewish singles find their soul mates, a task that is often long and difficult for many. Its success quickly established Frumster as the premier international Jewish dating service for sincere and marriage-minded singles. Since the launch of our service, 1312 members, a record number, have found a marriage partner through our site. A dedicated team of professionals based in New York City, screens prospective clients and works with members daily to create a quality Jewish internet dating service where sincere and respectful individuals may join and communicate with prospective matches in a private and discrete forum.

Frumster adheres to Orthodox values and consults with an Orthodox Rabbi to maintain service suitable for all Jews serious about finding a marriage partner and building a Jewish home.
